description: Data was generated from file metadata from all series information in the Cancer Imaging Archive (TCIA) from June 2017. http://www.cancerimagingarchive.net/#collections-list

fields.description: Each series is part of a study. This field contains the unique study identifier. Example: 1.3.6.1.4.1.22213.2.26555
fields.name: StudyInstanceUID

fields.description: Image/file modality.The most common values are MR and CT, but there are many other types,including SEG, RTSTRUCT, etc
fields.name: Modality

fields.description: This field is frequently blank, but otherwise is of the form YYYY-MM-DD.
fields.name: SeriesDate

fields.description: This field can be blank,but otherwise contains a free-text description. Examples:AXIAL T1 SI LOCALIZER, Maximum eigenvalue, Average DC
fields.name: SeriesDescription

fields.description: This field can be blank. The most common values are PROSTATE, BREAST, BRAIN, LUNG, etc
fields.name: BodyPartExamined

fields.description: A relatively arbitrary series identifier, intended to be more human-readable than the series UID. Examples: 676.0, 2.0, 8.0, 401.0
fields.name: SeriesNumber

fields.description: Unique collection name. Examples:TCGA-GBM, IvyGAP, QIN-HEADNECK, REMBRANDT, etc
fields.name: Collection

fields.description: This field may be blank. The most common values are SIEMANS and GE MEDICAL SYSTEMS. Other possible values include QIICR, Philips, TOSHIBA, etc
fields.name: Manufacturer

fields.description: This field may be blank. The most common values are Skyra and GENESIS_SIGNA.
fields.name: ManufacturerModelName

fields.description: This field may be blank. Examples: 02, 08, 11, A10, AWS, 3.33, 6.3.9
fields.name: SoftwareVersions

fields.description: The number of images in this series. The most common values are 16 and 1, but the value can be over 1000.
fields.name: ImageCount

fields.description: Frequently left blank, but otherwise a free form text description of the protocol. Examples: 6.8 TRI-PHASIC LIVER, 6.12 AORTA, Survey_SHC, Survey_SHC
fields.name: ProtocolName

fields.description: This field is usually blank, and otherwise set to 1. That is, the value is always either null or 1.
fields.name: AnnotationsFlag
